      <title>高盛团队找到替代拥挤台积电套利交易的方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/goldman-team-finds-alternative-to-crowded-tsmc-arbitrage-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这已成为华尔街套利者最受欢迎且近期最痛苦的交易之一：买入台湾半导体制造公司估值较低的台北股票，并做空美国股票，希望价格能够趋于一致。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-20/goldman-team-finds-alternative-to-crowded-tsmc-arbitrage-trade</guid>
